  "description": "This test case evaluates identification of a complex anxiety phenotype requiring multiple clinical data elements: longitudinal EHR history (365+ days), age restrictions (741+ days at last visit, approximately 2 years), multiple anxiety-related encounters on different days, and evidence of treatment through medications or procedures. It tests the system's ability to handle multi-criteria phenotype algorithms with temporal constraints and treatment evidence requirements.",
